values: I started to calm down right before Vasquez put up the list...wehn she was giving that speech(which is odd) well it just reassured me and i didn't even get up to go check the list! WEll yea as you all told me i did make it-bass #4 again! that's cool! Rudy and Cristian replaced both Mikes...Icky's on Snare and Mikey is gone off to play football so.... well whatever, hope the show doesn't suck...wel ig2g to practice!

Hey guys...i'm kinda bummed out/worried! Tomarrow Vasquez said that she was going to tell us what we're gona play this year and who's on the line...but i'm scared to death that my name isn't going to be on that list! All the ppl in the hall...as i'm going to refer to all like 8 of 'em...said i have nothing to worry about (even Mike aka Icky)b/c i've got 2 yrs marching experience and 3 yrs w/ the band and i'm good at bass! Plus Vasquez said i was an "awesome bass drummer" but still she also said that i need to work on snare b/c "it's the same thing as bass only flipped over" blah blah blah but yea!and that part really freaks me out! What would happen if by chance i didn't make it...man i doubt i'd quit,but to be in pit again, shit! i don't want that, it's so boring and crappy-no offense! idunno!But i'm really freaked out! well i guess we'll just see what happens tomarrow right! well laterz
Happy Thursday everyone......yea i just felt like typing one last thing before i get off! laterzzzzzzzzzzzzzzzz
I just wanted to say Happy birthday to David...taht's all i have to say! oh and Thank you lovesredwine...you made me feel so much better about things this morning and hopefully it only gets gooder!

I'm sorry if i sound...blah, i'm in one of those hyper moods, lol when am i not, right! well Today's been good, just cause, but i've been oddly tired and when i tried to take a nap i couldn't except for those first initial 5 min and those 5 min right before my mom woke me up to go get Carlos for church....so yea when you saw me i had just woken up! lol Well it's time to eat so i must leave my fine feathered friends.....i told you i'm not right today! lol! maybe it's the room i'm in.....hehehehe Well to all the fathers that readthis(hopefully none...yet) Feliz Dia de los Padres! lol yea i'm bilangual!!!(i just can't spelll it!)lol! bye

I dunno! but i'll just write for awhile before i go to sleep! Tomarrow i gotta get up at about 9:30 so i can finally have that interview at Stars....it's odd how i promised myself that i'd never work in fast food, but dang peerpressure from Bob....lol! well im too lazy to find something outside of the food industry so it'll do fine, that is if i do actually get the job!

Well over a month later Ms. Mora has come back! well it's only tow weeks, hopefully she forgot about the finals or something though! lol yea right!
Newayz, today i went to go get my license and my mom got me out early from school so she could take me to Weslaco and guess what they tell me i need to go tomarrow!!! ahh i guess right, but the thing is this means i get out of BCIS for 2 days and i was suppose to work on a presentation that's due tomarrow, i can't really do it here but i guess whatever i got should be good enough, i'll just make a quick one, hopefully that's good enough!
How many times did i accidently put the same entry up..man i had to cut them out! well i guess i could've left 'em but...na!

Well Today was a good change! It wasn't great but I can't complain about it! Andy gave my twizzlers, yummmy, thanks Andy!!!! It was so awesome b/c when I got to my fifth period class Ms. Mora still isn't back yet, so cool-even if the sub looks at me weird! ah and today i asked him for change to go get a coke but he was being a butt abou it and said until he saw me doing my work , after i was halfway done(that is if you don't count the 1 page crap!)but he eventually gave my change- i think he was just playing around though...it is better than having her back, eek but next week! uhhh, whatelse happened today! Ooooh, David brought me back a penny from Houston, it's one of those looney toons pennys that they flatten! oh yea! lol! ***Hey guys, i'm confused-when is State solo and ensemble, b/c I'm hearing the Monday after school ends and then i'm hearing Friday!!! I swear they first told us that it was on the following monday...i hope it's on the Monday so i can go to a Graduation party on Friday, that's gonna suck b/c i've been looking forward to it!!!! Well that is if the directors let me go..i haven't been practicing my solo...eek! Well i guess that's all that really happend today! oh and before i forget, who has Ms. Dickenson-is anyone actually doing that project???

Well i don't plan on writing too much, but i say that an i know i'll end up writing this super duper long entry! well i'm just here talking to David on AIM! Newayz, today we finally finished all the TAks tests, for this year, and it's a huge relief, although not going to class was fun, it didn't take me long i finished around 9:30 and it didn't take me long after to fall asleep, that is until it started to get loud and Trisha woke me up at about 11! But that's okay! Well TOmarrow is gonna suck, not only are the teachers gonnna want to go back to regular teaching but i'm gonna be all lonely b/c most ppl are going on the band trip, so i'll be sad! Oh well! well i'm getting sleepy so i'll just write later tomarrow.!   by~the~way

I dunno I AM a dork, what else can I say,  those of you who know me already learned that early on! lol! well after a couple of  hours at the mall we took another hour at RAdio shack and then finally went to Lesylle's thing! OOH, if  by any chance Lesylle's mom or whoever made that food is reading, it was GOOOOOOOD, I want more of the brisket and rice, yuuuuuuummmmyy  (Now I have a rumbly in my tumbly) and for you Visual learners There will soon be tons(only 3) pictures of  it  on Patty's live journal, so if you wanna see 'em bug her about 'em till she puts 'em up! Well, that's basically what I did today, sadly that's the most exciting thing that's happend in a while...not true, I did get to see David's Underware the other day, hehehe ewe that was so scary!!!lol sorry about that DAvid!

Oh yea, I told David that I was gonna tell everyone about what I saw today! (hehehe)Well today we were finally taking our band picture, so during lunch David, Trisha, and me decided we were gonna do it during lunch. Well when we went Trisha had left to the Bathroom to change, but me and David decided to just put the uniform over our clothes rather than have to go to the restroom. Well I guess David's uniform was too tight to wear his jeans under so he went behind the counter thing in the locker room and started to take his pants off(No one was there to see).  Well i didn't hear him say he was gonna take of his pants(Honestly, i thought he was joking when he moved) well i walked around and yup I saw David's UNDERWARE!!! ewe-and for all of you that want to know, they were black boxer/briefs! I'm just glad i didn't see anymore than that!Fabian your next!!!! lol
